{
    "en": {
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "Lee: Hyperreal is a technical ground character with difficult-to-master gameplay. He focuses entirely on damage at the expense of his own survivability.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_SUBTITLE": "Simulation complete... Commander, we will win this fight.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_LORE": "\"Are the tests going well?\"\n\nThe crisp footsteps of expensive shoes echoed too loudly in the medicinally sterile chambers.\n\n\"Yes, sir. Did you feel that just now?\"\n\nThe deep hum of energy that swept across the disinfected floors vibrated against the shoes, the expensive pair and the worn pair.\n\n\"That was a weapons test, sir. A portable weapon.\"\n\nThis made the footsteps hesitate. \"Portable?\"\n\n\"Yes, sir. It has evolved greatly since your last visit.\"\n\n\"Hrm. Well, the weapons won't mean much if the subject is another defect. Are we close?\"\n\n\"Yes, sir, it's this way.\"\n\nThe worn shoes, stained with chemicals and burned by malfunctions, stepped forward, and trembling hands reached for a card given to him for the day. They knew he would be a bundle of nerves, but that fed the guest's ego, which meant a happier visit.\n\nA single swipe, a retinal scan that had just been granted access, and they were in a room neither had seen before.\n\n\"Is that an it? Or a him?\"\n\nWords from a memorized infographic filled his head. \"It's both, sir. The biosynthesis worked perfectly, unlike the previous tests. It's a perfect combination.\"\n\n\"I see. So it's organic?\"\n\n\"It's cybernetic, but correct. And it wasn't easy, sir. Like growing a square watermelon with natural selection.\"\n\n\"Yes, yes, I understand. The funds will be transferred upon my return.\"\n\n\"Thank you, sir.\"\n\nThe expensive shoes turned to leave, but were stopped by a sudden thought. \"Say, you've tested it, right?\"\n\nA nervous gulp, an unexpected question. \"Hm? Oh, uh, no, I don't think we've tested it.\"\n\n\"Hm. Well, sort that out, or I'll have to consider it a risk. You don't want to repeat the last mistake, do you?\"\n\nThe bitter words made the worn shoes hesitate, and an access card trembled inside an acid-burned hand. \"No, Mr. Wade. We don't. We'll send the live test footage to your dec... (line truncated to 2000 chars)",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..and then he left, still no closer to his true reality.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..and then he vanished, with a mission unfulfilled.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_SURVIVOR_POD_EXIT": "Cross Dimension",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_DEFAULT_SKIN_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ALT_SKIN_NAME": "Lee: Real",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_SCARLET_SKIN_NAME": "Lee: Scarlet Redeemer",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PROSPECTOR_SKIN_NAME": "Prospector",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PROSPECTOR_ALT_SKIN_NAME": "Comrade",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_YI_SKIN_NAME": "Yi",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_BK_SKIN_NAME": "Boykisser",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_ORB_AND_AMMO_NAME": "Orb and Ammo System",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_ORB_AND_AMMO_DESCRIPTION": "Lee: Hyperreal uses <style=cIsUtility>[Orbs]</style> that allow the execution of unique skills. His <style=cIsUtility>[Ammo Counter]</style> grants unique effects for <style=cIsUtility>[Sniper Stance]</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_DOMAIN_NAME": "Hypermatrix System",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_DOMAIN_DESCRIPTION": "Lee: Hyperreal has access to the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style> when holding the Primary button with the <style=cIsUtility>[Power Gauge]</style> full. Lee: Hyperreal gains more hits instead of attack speed, however Sniper Stance scales normally.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_VFX_COLOR_NAME": "VFX Color",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_DEFAULT_VFX_NAME": "Default VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_DEFAULT_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to the default based on skin choice.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_RED_VFX_NAME": "Red VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_RED_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to Red.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_ORANGE_VFX_NAME": "Orange VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_ORANGE_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to Orange.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_YELLOW_VFX_NAME": "Yellow VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_YELLOW_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to Yellow.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_GREEN_VFX_NAME": "Green VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_GREEN_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to Green.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_BLUE_VFX_NAME": "Blue VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_BLUE_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to Blue.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_LIGHTBLUE_VFX_NAME": "Light Blue VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_LIGHTBLUE_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to Light Blue.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_VIOLET_VFX_NAME": "Violet VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_VIOLET_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to Violet.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_PINK_VFX_NAME": "Pink VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_PINK_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Changes the VFX color to Pink.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_RAINBOW_VFX_NAME": "Rainbow VFX",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PASSIVE_RAINBOW_VFX_DESCRIPTION": "Randomly selects a VFX color.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PRIMARY_NAME": "Arms Barrage",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PRIMARY_DESCRIPTION": "Launch a 5-hit combo attack. On hits 1 and 3, execute a <style=cIsUtility>[Parry]</style> active for a short period. In the air, slam downward dealing <style=cIsDamage>400% damage</style>, increasing up to <style=cIsDamage>3x</style> based on distance traveled. Hold the button at any time with the <style=cIsUtility>[Power Gauge]</style> full to enter the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ENTER_SNIPE_NAME": "Sniper Stance",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ENTER_SNIPE_DESCRIPTION": "Enter <style=cIsUtility>[Sniper Stance]</style>, immobilizing you in place, allowing you to use Snipe with Primary for <style=cIsDamage>400% damage</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_EXIT_SNIPE_NAME": "Exit Sniper Stance",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_EXIT_SNIPE_DESCRIPTION": "Exit <style=cIsUtility>[Sniper Stance]</style>, allowing you to move again.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_SECONDARY_SNIPE_NAME": "Snipe",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_SECONDARY_SNIPE_DESCRIPTION": "Fire a bullet dealing <style=cIsDamage>400% damage</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_DASH_NAME": "Reality Traveler",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_DASH_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Dodge</style>, becoming invulnerable for a short period.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ULTIMATE_NAME": "End of Times",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ULTIMATE_DESCRIPTION": "Become invulnerable, pulling out a cannon that explodes enemies in a wide radius for <style=cIsDamage>6,500% damage</style> after a brief charge. Your moves change while in the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ULTIMATE_DOMAIN_NAME": "Collapsing Realm",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ULTIMATE_DOMAIN_DESCRIPTION": "Collapse the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style>, becoming invulnerable for a short period and dealing <style=cIsDamage>1,500% damage</style> in your wake. Each 3-Ping during the hypermatrix adds 3 hits of <style=cIsDamage>200% damage</style> to <style=cIsUtility>[Collapsing Realm]</style>. Maximum of 4 times for 12 extra hits.</i>",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ITEM_EFFECT_TITLE": "Hyper Effect",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ITEM_EFFECT_BACKUPMAG_DESC": "<style=cIsDamage>Lee: Hyperreal</style> gains <style=cIsUtility>+1</style> <style=cStack>(+1 per stack)</style> Reinforced bullet(s) on each successful <style=cIsUtility>[Parry]</style>.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ITEM_EFFECT_ALIEN_HEAD_DESC": "<style=cIsDamage>Lee: Hyperreal's</style> orbs charge <style=cIsUtility>25% faster</style>.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ITEM_EFFECT_PURITY_DESC": "<style=cIsDamage>Lee: Hyperreal's</style> orb recharge rate is reduced by <style=cIsUtility>2</style> <style=cStack>(+1 per stack)</style> seconds.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ITEM_EFFECT_ATTACK_SPEED_DESC": "<style=cIsDamage>Lee: Hyperreal's</style> primary gains more <style=cIsUtility>hits</style> instead of attack speed. Ex: 250% attack speed = 2 hits and a half-damage hit.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_ITEM_EFFECT_LUMINOUS_SHOT_DESC": "<style=cIsDamage>Lee: Hyperreal's</style> Sniper Stance shots grant <style=cIsUtility>1 Stack</style> per shot instead of using the Secondary.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_KEYWORD_ORBS": "<style=cKeywordName>Orb System</style>\nLee: Hyperreal uses 3 Orbs of different colors to use extra skills. In Simple Mode, activate <style=cIsUtility>Blue</style>, <style=cIsUtility>Red</style> and <style=cIsUtility>Yellow</style> orbs using the designated keys, to use the first group of colored orbs from left to right. Using 3 adjacent orbs of the same color, known as <style=cIsUtility>[3-ping]</style>, increases the orb skill's damage by <style=cIsDamage>4x</style>, in addition to granting extra attacks for <style=cIsUtility>Red</style> and <style=cIsUtility>Yellow</style> Orbs.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_KEYWORD_AMMO": "<style=cKeywordName>Ammo System</style>\nLee: Hyperreal can store and use a variety of <style=cIsUtility>Ammo</style>, indicated above the <style=cIsUtility>[Power Gauge]</style>. Using a <style=cIsUtility>[3-ping]</style> will store a <style=cIsUtility>[Colored Bullet]</style>, which can be used in the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style> to add 3 Orbs of that color back to your <style=cIsUtility>[Orb System]</style> when using Snipe during it. On a successful <style=cIsUtility>[Parry]</style>, <style=cIsUtility>[Reinforced Bullets]</style> are granted, increasing the damage of your next shot in <style=cIsUtility>[Sniper Stance]</style> by <style=cIsDamage>2x</style>.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_KEYWORD_SNIPE_STANCE": "<style=cKeywordName>Sniper Stance</style>\nEnter a posture that immobilizes you, changing your Primary Skill to a precision shot dealing <style=cIsDamage>400% damage</style> per shot. Using the Utility Skill without any directional input allows you to dodge backward while firing a bullet dealing <style=cIsDamage>400% damage</style>. Using this skill otherwise cancels the posture.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_KEYWORD_POWER_GAUGE": "<style=cKeywordName>Power Gauge</style>\nThe Power Gauge located above the Health Bar determines when you can enter the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style>, and how much time remains before exiting. Hold the Primary Skill to enter the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style>.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_KEYWORD_PARRY": "<style=cKeywordName>Parry</style>\nOn a successful parry, stun the enemy that dealt the damage if it can be stunned. Any parried projectile will be shot back in the direction you aim. A successful parry resets <style=cIsUtility>[Arms Barrage]</style>, starting from the move used to parry again.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_KEYWORD_DOMAIN": "<style=cKeywordName>Hypermatrix System</style>\nAbove your Health is the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix System Gauge]</style>. When the gauge is full, holding the Primary Skill at any time in <style=cIsUtility>[Arms Barrage]</style> will transport you to the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style>. In this state, <style=cIsUtility>Red</style> and <style=cIsUtility>Yellow</style> orbs change completely, and your Special becomes <style=cIsUtility>[Collapsing Realm]</style>. If the gauge expires in this state, <style=cIsUtility>[Collapsing Realm]</style> will be activated automatically, exiting the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style>.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_KEYWORD_DOMAIN_ULT": "<style=cKeywordName>Collapsing Realm</style>\nCollapse the <style=cIsUtility>[Hypermatrix]</style>, becoming invulnerable for a short period and dealing <style=cIsDamage>1,500% damage</style> in your wake. Add 3 hits of <style=cIsDamage>200% damage</style> each time you use a <style=cIsUtility>[3-ping]</style> in the hypermatrix. Maximum of 4 times for 12 extra hits.",
        "LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_BROTHER_RESPONSE_ENTRY": "How did you get here?",
        "LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_BROTHER_RESPONSE_ON_DEATH_1": "Pray in your own dimension.",
        "LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_BROTHER_RESPONSE_ON_DEATH_2": "Another reality won't save you from me.",
        "LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_BROTHER_RESPONSE_ON_DEATH_3": "I will crush every copy of you.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_MASTERYUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_MASTERYUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Lee: Hyperreal, beat the game or obliterate yourself on Monsoon.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_MASTERYUNLOCKABLE_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_BLUESKIN_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Real",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_BLUESKIN_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Lee: Hyperreal, beat the game on Monsoon with Transcendence, or roll 5% chance from a Medium or higher chest.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_BLUESKIN_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Real",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_SCARLET_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Scarlet",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_SCARLET_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Lee: Hyperreal, beat the game on Monsoon without clock items and bleed, or roll 5% chance from a Legendary chest.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_SCARLET_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Scarlet",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_YELLOW_VFX_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Yellow VFX",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_YELLOW_VFX_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Lee: Hyperreal, beat the game on Monsoon with 5+ Boss items, or roll 2% chance from any chest.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_YELLOW_VFX_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Yellow VFX",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_GREEN_VFX_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Green VFX",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_GREEN_VFX_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Lee: Hyperreal, beat the game on Monsoon with 15+ healing items, or roll 2% chance from any chest.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_GREEN_VFX_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Green VFX",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PINK_VFX_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Pink VFX",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PINK_VFX_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Lee: Hyperreal, kill the Teleporter boss with End of Times at max power, or roll 2% chance from any chest.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_PINK_VFX_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Pink VFX",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_VIOLET_VFX_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Violet VFX",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_VIOLET_VFX_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Lee: Hyperreal, beat the game on Eclipse 8, or roll 1% chance from a Legendary chest.",
        "POPCORN_LEE_HYPERREAL_BODY_VIOLET_VFX_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Lee: Hyperreal: Violet VFX"
    }
}
